          "reviewText": "Great Coverage and Natural Finish The Fit Me Foundation is amazing! It provides smooth, buildable coverage without feeling heavy or cakey. The finish looks natural and blends easily into my skin, giving a flawless look that lasts throughout the day. It matches my skin tone really well, and I\u2019ve noticed it works nicely for both everyday wear and special occasions. Affordable, high-quality, and definitely worth trying!",
