        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great product!",
          "reviewText": "I really like this Maybelline Fit Me Matte + Poreless foundation and I\u2019m giving it 4 stars. The shade Soft Tan matches my skin beautifully and gives a natural, smooth finish. It\u2019s lightweight and feels comfortable on the skin without feeling heavy or cakey. I noticed that it helps minimize the look of pores and controls oil throughout the day, which is great for my combination skin. The coverage is buildable, so it\u2019s easy to go from a light everyday look to more coverage where I need it. I\u2019m not giving it 5 stars only because the wear time isn\u2019t quite as long as some higher-end foundations I\u2019ve tried, and it can fade a bit by the end of the day. Still, for the price and quality, it\u2019s a foundation I\u2019m happy to keep in my makeup routine.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2025",
